07:04.200 --> 07:06.800
Better have our passports ready.

07:06.800 --> 07:10.300
This is the first time rock music
has been allowed in this country.

07:10.300 --> 07:15.300
You're not just a performer. You're
an ambassador representing America.

07:15.300 --> 07:18.100
And above all, we play by their rules.

07:18.100 --> 07:24.800
Martin, I've been practising. How's this?
<i>Ist Ihre Tochter achtzehn, bitte?</i>

07:25.100 --> 07:28.300
- What does that mean?
- Is your daughter 18?

07:33.100 --> 07:35.400
Your papers, please.

07:41.200 --> 07:43.500
Mr. Nick Rivers.

07:43.500 --> 07:47.000
